---
title: Hot Honey Baked Salmon with Garlic Rice and Soy Fried Veg
description: Salmon is a delicate and flavoursome fish, perfect for absorbing the flavour of the hot honey in this recipe. Paired with garlicky rice and soy fried mangetout and mushrooms, it's a real catch!
